version_description:
This app has been updated by Apple to use the latest Apple signing certificate.

*** We would like to improve our app with your help, if you find a bug please contact us at www.ordotmobile.com/contact so we can solve the issue instead of leaving a negative comment. Thank you ***

* Tested on multiple iOS9 devices
* Solved issue with sounds not working on certain devices
* Several bug fixes
* Improved performance
